you find me a professor anywhere in north america that can handle 3,169 questions _ and they weren't stupid questions,'' phillips said
students who miss phillips' lecture on the first day of class can only guess at the appearance of the professor known by his computer address ``gmp.''
one says she's going to track me down to see what i look like and talk to me face to face. i said `catch me if you can,''' said phillips
