it's like e-mail is god,'' she said. ``it really shouldn't bere has to be some communication that is one-on-one.''
others disagree
i don't think we've suffered any because we e like that. thhaven't seen him face to face,'' said michael guerin, a senior operations management major from rochester, n.y. ``he's readily available on the computer.''
