the past couple of witching hours have been relatively uneventful with the adoption of new procedures designed to spread out the impact of last-minute maneuvering by computer program traders
on the actives list, airline issues were up amid reports that a number of carriers plan to tighten restrictions on discount fares. allegis rose 1| to 79{, amr rose 1| to 42|, and southwest airlines was up ] to 17\
