on the opening, wheat was unchanged to { cent lower with the contract for delivery in july at $3.07 a bushel; corn was unchanged to \ cent higher with march at $1.98{ a bushel; oats were unchanged to { cent higher with march at $1.90\ a bushel; and soybeans were { cent lower to } cent higher with march at $6.14\ a bushel
